---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about HavenKeep's mission to help people protect their purchases and never lose track of warranties">
  <Navigation />
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-gray-800">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Protecting What Matters
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300">
            We're on a mission to help people take control of their warranties and never lose track of their purchases
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Story Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              HavenKeep was born from a simple frustration: losing a warranty when you need it most. Like many people, our founders had experienced the panic of searching through stacks of papers and old emails trying to find proof of purchase for a broken appliance, only to discover the warranty had expired last month.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              We knew there had to be a better way. In 2024, we set out to build the warranty tracking app we wished existed - one that was simple, powerful, and actually worked the way people think. No complicated spreadsheets, no filing systems, just point, snap, and protect.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Today, over 1,200 users trust HavenKeep to protect their purchases. From homeowners tracking appliances to small businesses managing equipment warranties, we're helping people save time, money, and stress.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-12">Our Values</h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <!-- Value 1 -->
            <div class="p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg bg-gray-900">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Simple by Default</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                We believe great software should be invisible. You shouldn't need a manual to protect your purchases.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Value 2 -->
            <div class="p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg bg-gray-900">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Privacy First</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Your data is yours. We use encryption everywhere and never sell your information.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Value 3 -->
            <div class="p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg bg-gray-900">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Customer Obsessed</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Every feature we build starts with understanding your needs. Your feedback drives our roadmap.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Value 4 -->
            <div class="p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg bg-gray-900">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Built to Last</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                We're building a company for the long term, not just chasing the next trend.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-12">Meet the Team</h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Team Member 1 -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">JD</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1">Jane Doe</h3>
              <p class="text-primary mb-2">Co-Founder & CEO</p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
                Former product lead at a major tech company, passionate about consumer rights
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Team Member 2 -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary to-accent rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">MS</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1">Mike Smith</h3>
              <p class="text-primary mb-2">Co-Founder & CTO</p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
                15 years in mobile development, loves building things that just work
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Team Member 3 -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-primary rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">SK</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1">Sarah Kim</h3>
              <p class="text-primary mb-2">Head of Design</p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
                Award-winning designer focused on making complex things simple
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-12 text-center">
            <a href="/careers" class="inline-block text-primary hover:text-secondary font-semibold">
              We're hiring! Join our team â†’
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
            Join 1,200+ happy users
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8">
            Start protecting your warranties today
          </p>
          <a href="https://app.havenkeep.com/signup" class="inline-block bg-white text-primary hover:bg-gray-100 font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 text-lg">
            Get Started Free
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
